    "notes": "\"Why the generated weapon doesn't match the example in the Field Catalogue\\n\\n- The manifest in the book has a base weight of 1kg for an assault receiver but the rules say it's 2kg (p31)\\n- The manifest in the book doesn't have the 20% receiver cost reduction for light handgun calibre (p36)\\n- The manifest in the book has a 20% receiver weight reduction for light handgun calibre but the rules say it's 25% (p36)\\n- The manifest in the book has a 20% ammo capacity reduction for the compact feature but the rules say it's 25% (p33), the result is the final ammo capacity is given as 13 when it should be 12\\n- The manifest in the book doesn't have the Quickdraw +2 modifier for an assault weapon with no stock (p43)\\n- The weapon description in the book says that the magazine cost is calculated differently to the standard rules as it uses commercially available magazines.\\n\\n\""
